title: KYLIN-5082,exactly match for percentile
body:
## Proposed changes

Refer to this: https://github.com/apache/kylin/pull/1619. For percentile function exactly match.

## Test Evidence

SQL: 

```
SELECT LO_SUPPKEY, percentile_approx(LINEORDER.LO_ORDTOTALPRICE, 0.5) AS ORDER_TOTAL_PRICE
FROM SSB.LINEORDER
GROUP BY LO_SUPPKEY
```
